  "difficultyLevel": 5,
  "lyrics": "Are you good to you, are you good to you In the night, night, night, it comes I wake up, am I good to me? I got all the best advice, do I take it? Nah, not me, I wake up and I'm good to me That's a laughing fact and laughing stock of history Of my mind, inside my mind, I look back on the times I could've been there for me, but I wasn't Lost my shit, lost all my stuff, done drowning in emotions Don't, don't, don't, don't fit today A little single child occupancy inside my brain Makes me always wanna make the one to please To reach out to fix the hole to be there next to me I guess I stole it from the night inside of my mind I just know it's hard for me to be good to me So I'm asking you to help me try Be good to you, be good to me Be good to you, so you can be good to me Sometimes at night I see it lost, like a line inside my mind Where there was generosity and kind inside of minds Inside of eyes that I see on the street I see nothing but pain and ego Vortex curiosity of insane When I see lights, I see me, so be good to you When I see you, I see me, try to be good to me You see, golden rule way I'll be good to you, you be good to me I'll be good if you're good to me Lightning strikes only once in this life And from that spark becomes a different thing Embracing of all, we say Ten percent to change Have it be another way Ten percent to change Don't happen So be good to you, be good to me Be good to you, be good to me Be good enough to adjust to my frame To just say don't take the thing from the thing No violence here But let's play a puzzle game It's the show",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 18.780000686645508,
      "text": "Are you good to you, are you good to you In the night, night, night, it comes",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 24.399999618530273,
      "text": "I wake up, am I good to me?",
      "start": 20.100000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 29.260000228881836,
      "text": "I got all the best advice, do I take it?",
      "start": 25.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 34.060001373291016,
      "text": "Nah, not me, I wake up and I'm good to me",
      "start": 29.280000686645508
    },
    {
      "end": 39.70000076293945,
      "text": "That's a laughing fact and laughing stock of history",
      "start": 35.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 43.040000915527344,
      "text": "Of my mind, inside my mind, I look back on the times",
      "start": 39.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 45.599998474121094,
      "text": "I could've been there for me, but I wasn't",
      "start": 43.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 50.08000183105469,
      "text": "Lost my shit, lost all my stuff, done drowning in emotions",
      "start": 45.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 52.70000076293945,
      "text": "Don't, don't, don't, don't fit today",
      "start": 50.29999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 56.18000030517578,
      "text": "A little single child occupancy inside my brain",
      "start": 52.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 59.81999969482422,
      "text": "Makes me always wanna make the one to please",
      "start": 56.560001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 63.36000061035156,
      "text": "To reach out to fix the hole to be there next to me",
      "start": 59.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 68.23999786376953,
      "text": "I guess I stole it from the night inside of my mind",
      "start": 63.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 73.95999908447266,
      "text": "I just know it's hard for me to be good to me",
      "start": 68.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 78.54000091552734,
      "text": "So I'm asking you to help me try",
      "start": 73.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 89.37999725341797,
      "text": "Be good to you, be good to me",
      "start": 79.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 98.63999938964844,
      "text": "Be good to you, so you can be good to me",
      "start": 90.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 104.91999816894531,
      "text": "Sometimes at night I see it lost, like a line inside my mind",
      "start": 100.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 109.13999938964844,
      "text": "Where there was generosity and kind inside of minds",
      "start": 105.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 112.18000030517578,
      "text": "Inside of eyes that I see on the street",
      "start": 109.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 114.95999908447266,
      "text": "I see nothing but pain and ego",
      "start": 112.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 119.63999938964844,
      "text": "Vortex curiosity of insane",
      "start": 115.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 124.04000091552734,
      "text": "When I see lights, I see me, so be good to you",
      "start": 119.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 128.25999450683594,
      "text": "When I see you, I see me, try to be good to me",
      "start": 124.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 130.36000061035156,
      "text": "You see, golden rule way",
      "start": 128.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 134.9600067138672,
      "text": "I'll be good to you, you be good to me",
      "start": 130.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 139.63999938964844,
      "text": "I'll be good if you're good to me",
      "start": 135.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 146.36000061035156,
      "text": "Lightning strikes only once in this life",
      "start": 139.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 152.02000427246094,
      "text": "And from that spark becomes a different thing",
      "start": 149.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 158.16000366210938,
      "text": "Embracing of all, we say",
      "start": 153.02000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 161.66000366210938,
      "text": "Ten percent to change",
      "start": 158.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 167.77999877929688,
      "text": "Have it be another way",
      "start": 162.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 171.5,
      "text": "Ten percent to change",
      "start": 167.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 175.97999572753906,
      "text": "Don't happen",
      "start": 173.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 184.16000366210938,
      "text": "So be good to you, be good to me",
      "start": 179.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 189.25999450683594,
      "text": "Be good to you, be good to me",
      "start": 184.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 192.4199981689453,
      "text": "Be good enough to adjust to my frame",
      "start": 189.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 194.9600067138672,
      "text": "To just say don't take the thing from the thing",
      "start": 192.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 197.17999267578125,
      "text": "No violence here",
      "start": 195.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 199.3000030517578,
      "text": "But let's play a puzzle game",
      "start": 197.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 200.33999633789062,
      "text": "It's the show",
      "start": 199.3000030517578
    }
